From eaef2c62b47dbed387b2455f642ed0e0b425dbe1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nishant Sharma <nishant.sharma@arm.com>
Date: Thu, 28 Oct 2021 13:41:01 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 07/78] Platform/Sgi: generate pcie rootbridge topology layout
 dynamically

Add support to generate RootBridge layout dynamically from the topology
information passed to UEFI. Use a template to generate the basic layout
of the topology and then use the topology information to update
PcieHostBridgeLib specific datastructure.

This file is share by all the platforms on Sgi platforms, add a Pcd flag
to enable or disable this feature for the plarforms which does not use
this feature.

Signed-off-by: Nishant Sharma <nishant.sharma@arm.com>
Change-Id: I39d64bf56048e3509f379c6e22514fe12898b2c3
---
